Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}土\N豆\N蛋\N黄\N酱\N味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是名字的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧 素直 思考的重点不在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这解说也不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山同学 我们可以给这孩子吃点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像洋娃娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:03:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生就是爱这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么都说好可爱好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一点状况都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没有危机感了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来让我抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软软地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现在还在上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(100,150)\fs14}从上到下依次是: 面包菜单 咖喱面包 奶油面包 豆沙面包 炸肉面包 火腿肉三明治 鸡蛋三明治 巧克力卷 牛奶蛋糊派 巧克力丹麦包 囧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山素直同学中午总是吃面包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到他选什么面包后给他送去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我蜜柑的小小幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 森山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜单上有着看不见的秘密菜单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,250)\frz10\bord0\1c&H000000&\fs30}蜜柑自制便当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他能在那画上圈就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\1c&H000000&\fs30}素直他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\1c&H000000&\fs30}是蛋黄的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\1c&H000000&\fs30}人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦 蛋黄 不用谢我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买面包来还你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑日记 ○月X日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天终于与素直聊了面包以外的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天作为他说“那是你的便当吧”的纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会子子孙孙传颂下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选你喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到还有这家伙的份 就买多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 别老是恶作剧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山同学 面包很好吃啊 很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只有嫉妒的人才会说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高修在窗前看得目瞪口呆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿 才回到房间角落顺势倒躺在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼大睡起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 森山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你读下一段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三天晚上 高修依然拉着大提琴直到半夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉累了正勺水喝时 门外又传来叩叩敲门声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(100,150)\fs19}森山同学 森山同学 森山同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高修保持拿着杯子的姿势心想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚不管是谁会来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对都要像昨晚对待布谷鸟那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就先给个下马威轰走对方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那生物到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(100,150)\fs19}这里一直在重复“素直”这一名字 囧rz
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能像人那样发音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜 很便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(100,150)\fs19}大婶 给我两根萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天与森山同学说了许多话我感到很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,150)\fs19}好的 蜜柑 来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 该洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要加油做便当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该做些什么菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说蜜柑 你有听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该做些什么菜呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,70)\fs20\fr-2}汤汁鸡蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿床了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(165,165)\shad3\fad(300,300)}土豆2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,385)\shad3\fad(300,300)}来袭! 神秘的生物!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏会不够吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 森山同学你吃你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来你很意外的贪吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了给森山同学吃才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 竟然说我贪吃 贪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这贪吃鬼 脸上粘着饭咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的裙带菜 烤牛肉与麻婆豆腐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有虾汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都粘粘的了哦 蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会要借用下游泳部的浴室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 蛋黄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森山同学 就让她选自己喜欢的吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(0,200)}鸡\N蛋\N鱼\N松\N饭\N团
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 是鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同类相残
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么还这么看着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹦鹉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是雏鸟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶着鸟的蛋黄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先发试卷 大家按顺序来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿连
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石崎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时 在森山家里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到六点时是与上周一样是户外写生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要布置家庭作业 别随便回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 不要出这公园哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无道
